oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Christ Church Episcopal
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the exterior of Christ Church Episcopal in Rugby. There is an unidentified individual standing in the doorway, and another seated in a horse-drawn wagon on left. Handwriting at the bottom of the photograph reads: "Christ Church Episcopal - Rugby, Tennessee."
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
